00:28:03,679 --> 00:28:04,839
We finally got the box.

505
00:28:04,959 --> 00:28:05,919
My lady, what a scheme.

506
00:28:09,558 --> 00:28:10,639
Our efforts are not in vain.

507
00:28:11,879 --> 00:28:12,679
What is

508
00:28:12,919 --> 00:28:13,959
the hall's next step?

509
00:28:14,399 --> 00:28:15,959
Since you've gotten the box,

510
00:28:16,399 --> 00:28:17,919
you've protected Hua Wucuo.

511
00:28:18,718 --> 00:28:19,798
I'm sure

512
00:28:20,399 --> 00:28:21,278
the House of Sunset Drizzle

513
00:28:21,278 --> 00:28:22,839
will soon be crushed in the Capital.

514
00:28:25,119 --> 00:28:27,439
I asked my father to give me
half a month to get the box.

515
00:28:27,919 --> 00:28:29,359
At least I didn't let him down.

516
00:28:31,359 --> 00:28:32,399
But I heard

517
00:28:32,639 --> 00:28:34,399
Su Mengzhen is on his way back
to the Capital.

518
00:28:34,798 --> 00:28:36,278
Will our advantage

519
00:28:36,718 --> 00:28:39,399
be broken by his Red Sleeve Blade?

520
00:28:40,159 --> 00:28:41,119
My lady, don't worry.

521
00:28:41,439 --> 00:28:42,599
The main branch never planned

522
00:28:42,798 --> 00:28:44,639
to let Su Mengzhen return
to the Capital alive.

523
00:28:45,518 --> 00:28:47,278
They have already prepared
for his ambush.

524
00:28:47,718 --> 00:28:49,078
The Young Lady
of Wen Family can't die here.

525
00:28:49,879 --> 00:28:51,478
I will go and deal with the other two.

526
00:29:11,718 --> 00:29:12,478
My lady.

527
00:29:12,679 --> 00:29:13,199
You...

528
00:29:48,919 --> 00:29:49,518
(Kushuipu)
General Yang.

