00:29:49,519 --> 00:29:50,919
(Kushuipu)

530
00:29:50,919 --> 00:29:52,439
I've avenged you.

531
00:29:53,919 --> 00:29:54,919
Since this is where you departed,

532
00:29:55,439 --> 00:29:56,558
