533
00:30:13,718 --> 00:30:14,798
Cold breeze and freezing water.

534
00:30:15,639 --> 00:30:16,758
Aged yet still ambitious.

535
00:30:17,919 --> 00:30:19,318
A loyalty that doesn't
let the country down.

536
00:30:20,959 --> 00:30:22,639
A cup of liquor to send you off.

537
00:30:48,639 --> 00:30:49,439
Chun.

538
00:30:49,998 --> 00:30:50,639
Chun.

539
00:30:52,159 --> 00:30:53,399
Cabbage!

540
00:30:53,639 --> 00:30:54,278
Little Rock!

541
00:30:54,478 --> 00:30:55,599
Wake up!

542
00:30:55,758 --> 00:30:56,478
What time is it?

543
00:30:56,478 --> 00:30:57,558
Why are you still sleeping?

544
00:31:01,399 --> 00:31:02,478
Wake up.

545
00:31:03,639 --> 00:31:04,798
I was drunk.

546
00:31:06,679 --> 00:31:07,318
What's wrong?

547
00:31:07,558 --> 00:31:09,199
Both of you, go and wash up.

548
00:31:09,199 --> 00:31:10,238
I'm going to find Chun.

549
00:31:39,919 --> 00:31:40,758
Where's Chun?

550
00:31:41,478 --> 00:31:42,718
The three of you finally woke up.

551
00:31:43,119 --> 00:31:44,959
All of you were really drunk last night.

552
00:31:45,439 --> 00:31:47,078
I made some drinks
to cure your hangover.

553
00:31:48,199 --> 00:31:49,679
- Thank you.
- Thank you, Boatman.

554
00:31:50,238 --> 00:31:51,399
Where is Chun?

555
00:31:51,399 --> 00:31:53,159
Miss Tian and her subordinates

556
00:31:53,318 --> 00:31:54,679
got off the boat this morning.

557
00:31:55,078 --> 00:31:57,278
She said there was a change in schedule.

558
00:31:57,518 --> 00:31:58,119
Oh.

559
00:31:58,679 --> 00:32:00,798
She left you a note

560
00:32:00,798 --> 00:32:02,238
and asked me to pass it to you.

561
00:32:05,679 --> 00:32:06,798
(The path
of the martial arts world is long.)

562
00:32:07,199 --> 00:32:08,758
(We will meet again.)

563
00:32:09,159 --> 00:32:09,798
She really left?

564
00:32:26,558 --> 00:32:27,919
I really don't get it.

565
00:32:28,318 --> 00:32:29,839
She didn't even tell us in person

566
00:32:29,839 --> 00:32:30,679
and left.

567
00:32:31,238 --> 00:32:33,318
Didn't we have a lot of fun last night?

568
00:32:33,318 --> 00:32:34,399
You were really happy.

569
00:32:34,919 --> 00:32:36,599
It was because Miss Tian Chun
was being polite.

570
00:32:37,038 --> 00:32:38,758
But whether Miss Tian Chun
was happy or not,

571
00:32:39,478 --> 00:32:40,318
I don't know.

572
00:32:41,038 --> 00:32:42,278
What do you mean?

573
00:32:42,278 --> 00:32:43,478
Are you saying that I'm not polite?

574
00:32:44,119 --> 00:32:45,119
We boarded her boat

575
00:32:45,119 --> 00:32:46,359
and you still wanted
to sleep in her bed.

576
00:32:46,439 --> 00:32:47,399
Is that polite to you?

577
00:32:47,679 --> 00:32:48,478
I think Miss Tian Chun

578
00:32:48,478 --> 00:32:49,679
left without saying anything

579
00:32:49,679 --> 00:32:50,798
because you were impolite.

580
00:32:51,318 --> 00:32:52,919
That's where you are wrong.

581
00:32:53,238 --> 00:32:54,798
She invited me to sleep with her.

582
00:32:56,718 --> 00:32:57,478
I know.

583
00:32:57,879 --> 00:32:59,718
You are unhappy because Chun left.

584
00:32:59,718 --> 00:33:00,879
You like her, right?

585
00:33:01,478 --> 00:33:02,318
If you like her,

586
00:33:02,318 --> 00:33:03,718
just go and serve her.

587
00:33:04,518 --> 00:33:05,718
I can serve anyone I want.

588
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:07,439
I just don't like serving you.

589
00:33:07,639 --> 00:33:08,078
You...

590
00:33:08,078 --> 00:33:08,839
What?

591
00:33:09,199 --> 00:33:10,399
You can leave if my word hurts you.

592
00:33:10,558 --> 00:33:12,159
Wang Xiaoshi wants you here. Not me.

593
00:33:12,159 --> 00:33:13,758
Go away and don't annoy me.

594
00:33:14,238 --> 00:33:14,919
I'm telling you.

595
00:33:15,238 --> 00:33:17,359
People like you are not suitable
to roam the martial arts world.

596
00:33:17,478 --> 00:33:18,599
You are too spoiled for it.

597
00:33:19,078 --> 00:33:20,599
Return to Luoyang and be a Young Lady.

598
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:21,639
Darn Bai Choufei.

599
00:33:21,798 --> 00:33:22,879
I shouldn't have
treated you as my friend!

600
00:33:24,399 --> 00:33:25,599
Don't even think of seeing me again!

601
00:33:29,159 --> 00:33:31,038
No. You are treating her like this?

602
00:33:32,478 --> 00:33:34,278
There are two ways
of dealing with girls.

603
00:33:34,518 --> 00:33:35,758
One is being gentle
and another one is being tough.

604
00:33:36,078 --> 00:33:36,919
I only know the tough way.

605
00:33:37,679 --> 00:33:38,359
What about you?

606
00:33:39,199 --> 00:33:39,879
Didn't I...

607
00:33:40,879 --> 00:33:42,318
Didn't I go to the inn

608
00:33:42,318 --> 00:33:43,238
to get her the softest bed

609
00:33:43,238 --> 00:33:44,038
and the most expensive dishes?

610
00:33:46,238 --> 00:33:46,798
Forget it.

611
00:33:47,439 --> 00:33:48,599
She left from anger anyway.

612
00:33:49,318 --> 00:33:50,319
At least we achieved our goal.

613
00:33:53,478 --> 00:33:55,359
I blame it on the cursed box.

614
00:33:55,998 --> 00:33:57,839
We have to go to Kushuipu,
which is dangerous.

615
00:33:58,359 --> 00:33:59,478
It's better for her to leave.

616
00:34:00,439 --> 00:34:01,078
However,

617
00:34:01,319 --> 00:34:02,759
it might be difficult

618
00:34:02,998 --> 00:34:04,038
if you want her to return.

619
00:34:05,198 --> 00:34:05,719
It'll be hard for you.

620
00:34:05,959 --> 00:34:06,998
I need you to get her back.

621
00:34:07,678 --> 00:34:08,518
You are good with gentle methods.

622
00:34:10,598 --> 00:34:11,678
Why me?

623
00:34:12,719 --> 00:34:14,439
You were the one who made her angry.

624
00:34:14,959 --> 00:34:15,678
Don't go.

625
00:34:15,678 --> 00:34:17,518
Stupid Chou! Shameless!

626
00:34:17,998 --> 00:34:19,638
Little Rock! Stupid Rock!

627
00:34:20,038 --> 00:34:21,319
He didn't back me up.

628
00:34:22,478 --> 00:34:23,959
The most shameless Stupid Chou!

629
00:34:23,959 --> 00:34:25,078
The stupidest Little Rock!

630
00:34:25,198 --> 00:34:26,038
I'm so angry!

631
00:34:30,558 --> 00:34:31,118
No.

632
00:34:32,879 --> 00:34:33,558
Something's wrong.

633
00:34:49,039 --> 00:34:54,399
(Yang)

634
00:35:05,759 --> 00:35:08,118
You killed
a famous Liao general in the north.

635
00:35:09,239 --> 00:35:10,239
On your way down south,

636
00:35:10,558 --> 00:35:12,799
you also hit
a few Six Half Hall's branches.

637
00:35:13,959 --> 00:35:15,038
When we reach
the outskirts of the Capital,

638
00:35:15,719 --> 00:35:17,078
you need to keep a low profile.

639
00:35:18,158 --> 00:35:18,998
I'm keeping a low profile.

640
00:35:19,359 --> 00:35:20,839
How is this keeping a low profile?

641
00:35:21,158 --> 00:35:22,198
You are wearing a flaming red dress

642
00:35:22,439 --> 00:35:24,038
and sitting here heroically.

643
00:35:25,518 --> 00:35:27,799
Aren't you the greatest in the world?

644
00:35:28,919 --> 00:35:29,678
I am here

645
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:31,959
so the man with the box

646
00:35:32,319 --> 00:35:33,319
can find me.

647
00:35:35,799 --> 00:35:36,998
(Bun! Mantou!)

648
00:35:47,558 --> 00:35:48,959
Sir, I beg you.

649
00:35:49,118 --> 00:35:50,319
I starved for a few days.

650
00:35:50,359 --> 00:35:51,279
- Spare me some food.
- Go away!

651
00:35:51,558 --> 00:35:53,638
Stinking Beggar! Stop causing trouble!

652
00:35:58,998 --> 00:35:59,719
Hurry up!

653
00:36:05,879 --> 00:36:07,118
Kushuipu might be a mess,

654
00:36:07,678 --> 00:36:09,038
but there are masters
who are hiding around here too.

655
00:36:09,439 --> 00:36:10,598
It's a land of heroes.

656
00:36:11,638 --> 00:36:14,198
People of the martial arts world
fear this place out of respect.

657
00:36:14,719 --> 00:36:15,598
Not even people

658
00:36:16,279 --> 00:36:18,879
from House of Sunset Drizzle
and Six Half Hall

659
00:36:19,359 --> 00:36:20,478
would set foot in here usually.

660
00:36:22,759 --> 00:36:23,839
We have to be more careful then.

661
00:36:24,719 --> 00:36:25,319
That's right.

662
00:36:37,879 --> 00:36:40,041
(Yang)

663
00:37:20,853 --> 00:37:24,410
♪With whom do I visit this restaurant?♪

664
00:37:24,650 --> 00:37:28,210
♪The moonlit hall
stands within the clouds♪

665
00:37:29,048 --> 00:37:32,610
♪With whom do I ride my horse?♪

666
00:37:32,828 --> 00:37:36,410
♪The snow has blanched our attire♪

667
00:37:37,219 --> 00:37:40,730
♪In whom can I confide?♪

668
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:44,335
♪It's hard enough to find a true friend♪

669
00:37:45,453 --> 00:37:49,090
♪With whom do I drink?♪

670
00:37:49,227 --> 00:37:53,810
♪And who will tell me chug more?♪

671
00:37:54,359 --> 00:37:55,648
♪Don't tell me♪

672
00:37:55,812 --> 00:37:59,312
♪It's impossible, that sentiments
go in a blink of an eye♪

673
00:37:59,617 --> 00:38:03,312
♪That to stay out of it
is like an unreachable dream♪

674
00:38:03,391 --> 00:38:05,050
♪I'm glad to have you accompany me
on my journey♪

675
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:07,414
♪Begone, the thick evening mist♪

676
00:38:07,531 --> 00:38:10,850
♪We weathered through the storms♪

677
00:38:10,930 --> 00:38:11,922
♪Don't tell me♪

678
00:38:12,156 --> 00:38:15,610
♪It's impossible,
that time will always move on♪

679
00:38:15,898 --> 00:38:19,610
♪That the wish to leave behind a legacy
is just a wishful thinking♪

680
00:38:19,789 --> 00:38:24,010
♪I will find it, I will pierce through
the layers of fog♪

681
00:38:24,290 --> 00:38:28,563
♪I will not allow my life to be wasted♪

682
00:38:30,090 --> 00:38:32,130
♪One blade, one sword♪

683
00:38:32,203 --> 00:38:34,203
♪For my life, I have been wondering♪

684
00:38:34,289 --> 00:38:36,170
♪One lance, one arrow♪

685
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:38,082
♪A solitude and regretful life♪

686
00:38:38,359 --> 00:38:39,810
♪I discard my attire, I cut off my past♪

687
00:38:39,992 --> 00:38:42,130
♪Will happiness bloom?♪

688
00:38:42,210 --> 00:38:44,238
♪Perhaps I should get rid
of mortal desires♪

689
00:38:44,453 --> 00:38:49,750
♪They are the source of woes♪

690
00:38:49,867 --> 00:38:50,953
♪If♪

691
00:38:51,039 --> 00:38:54,850
♪It's possible, that sentiments don't
go in a blink of an eye♪

692
00:38:55,156 --> 00:38:58,770
♪That to stay out of it
isn't like an unreachable dream♪

693
00:38:58,867 --> 00:39:00,450
♪I'm glad to have you accompany me
on my journey♪

694
00:39:00,570 --> 00:39:03,031
♪Begone, the thick evening mist♪

695
00:39:03,250 --> 00:39:06,602
♪We will weather through the storms♪

696
00:39:06,797 --> 00:39:07,562
♪If♪

697
00:39:07,773 --> 00:39:11,170
♪It's possible,
that time can move slower♪

698
00:39:11,414 --> 00:39:14,970
♪That the wish to leave behind a legacy
isn't just a wishful thinking♪

699
00:39:15,195 --> 00:39:19,330
♪I found it, I pierced through
the layers of fog♪

700
00:39:19,672 --> 00:39:24,450
♪I will not allow my life to be wasted♪
